{"prompt": "Generate a sleek website for a management consulting firm. The brand color should be a distinguished charcoal grey.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Management Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: #f4f4f9;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal Grey */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal Grey */\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal Grey */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal Grey */\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .about-section {\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .about-section h2 {\n            color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal Grey */\n        }\n        .about-section p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            max-width: 900px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            color: #444;\n        }\n        .contact-section {\n            background-color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal Grey */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .contact-section h2 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important for padding */\n        }\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #34495e; /* Darker Charcoal */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #4b6a83; /* Slightly lighter charcoal */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        /* Responsive Adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .services-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Apex Management Consulting</h1>\n        <p>Strategic Solutions for Sustainable Growth.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Expertise</h2>\n        <div class=\"services-grid\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                <h3>Strategic Planning</h3>\n                <p>We help businesses define clear visions and actionable roadmaps for long-term success.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                <h3>Organizational Development</h3>\n                <p>Enhance team performance, leadership capabilities, and overall organizational health.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h3>Innovation & Transformation</h3>\n                <p>Drive change and foster innovation to stay ahead in dynamic markets.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-money-bill-trend-up\"></i>\n                <h3>Financial Strategy</h3>\n                <p>Optimize financial performance and develop robust strategies for profitability.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"about-section\">\n        <h2>About Apex</h2>\n        <p>Apex Management Consulting is dedicated to empowering organizations with the insights and strategies they need to navigate complex challenges and achieve their full potential. Our team of seasoned professionals brings a wealth of experience across diverse industries, committed to delivering tailored solutions that drive measurable results.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"contact-section\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\" action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n            <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Management Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add smooth scrolling for anchor links if needed\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}